  "title": "Site Admnistrator",
  "description": "<h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Minimum of 2 years’ relevant experience</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel, Outlook, etc.)</p></li></ul><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Develop and implement effective document control and management processes</p></li><li><p>Monitor document control processes to ensure compliance and accuracy</p></li><li><p>Set up and maintain project filing systems</p></li><li><p>Coordinate all activities related to Document Control procedures, including technical documents, drawings, and records for site materials and construction equipment</p></li><li><p>Generate and maintain document control reports as required by the project</p></li><li><p>Prepare and type site-related documents and follow up on site documentation needs</p></li><li><p>Ensure that controlled copies of the latest approved documents and drawings are distributed to relevant staff, subcontractors, and suppliers</p></li><li><p>Source suppliers for materials and other site-related orders</p></li><li><p>Maintain project files, registers, and control logs in accordance with project requirements</p></li><li><p>Perform ad hoc duties as assigned by the Project Manager and site team</p></li></ul>",
